headline: Qualcomm earned $215 target from BofA: Here’s what could derail it
summary: Bank of America is betting on Qualcomm's momentum by raising its price target from $200 to $215 and maintaining its buy rating. The analyst stated that Qualcomm recorded a “strong quarter with revenues up 10% vs Street's 5.1%, driven by 13.2% QCT growth vs Street's 7.7%.” The analyst note said ...
